        "id": "note_video_models",
        "type": "utility.note",
        "position": {
          "x": -520,
          "y": 20
        },
        "fields": {
          "body": "### Video model starter\n\nA quick reference workflow for the main video generation lanes. Each lane has its own group, preview node, and save node.\n\n- Kling 2.6 text to video creates a short video from a prompt only. [Model docs](https://docs.kie.ai/market/kling/kling-2.6-text-to-video.md)\n- Kling 2.6 image to video animates a selected source image into a short video. [Model docs](https://docs.kie.ai/market/kling/kling-2.6-image-to-video.md)\n\nRight-click a group title to enable or mute that lane. Keep only the lane you want to test enabled so you do not spend credits on every example at once.\n\nImage-to-video needs a source image selected in the Load Image node before running.\n\nHelpful links:\n\n- [Star Media Studio on GitHub](https://github.com/gateway/media-studio)\n- [GitHub issues](https://github.com/gateway/media-studio/issues)\n- [Model credits](https://kie.ai?ref=e7565cf24a7fad4586341a87eaf21e42)\n"
        },
        "metadata": {
          "style": {
            "width": 620,
            "height": 520
          },
          "ui": {
            "collapsed": false,
            "advancedExpanded": false,
            "accentColor": "#75a7f5",
            "nodeColor": "#172135",
            "nodeHeaderColor": "#1c2e46",
